<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/Granulometry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "MINNERSA, SGS\nIn this case, it is the classification of a mineral's size. A particle size analysis determines the proportion of minerals in different fractions. This is an important characteristic when processing minerals." .
