<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/MitigationEnvironmentalImpactProcedure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/MitigationProcedure> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/MitigationEnvironmentalImpactProcedure> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/SocialAcceptanceProcedure> .
