<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/MonitoringRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
