# http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/PrimaryCrushingOperation
<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/PrimaryCrushingOperation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/PrimaryCrushingOperation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/MineralProcessingOperation> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/PrimaryCrushingOperation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "MWEI BREF : Process of reducing ore into smaller fragments to prepare it for further  processing and/or so that it can be transported to the processing plant. In \nunderground mines, the primary crusher is often located underground or at the \nentrance to the processing plant."@en .
# 
# http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/Procedure
